{"tid":1552264,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"真心唔明點解啲熱門點解個個係到屌人set rb","createTime":"2019-09-08T09:58:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-08T13:28:06.000Z","uid":150031,"like":33,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"33bbd50148d7aebcdb01e504bf322ec2a51ffad4","tid":1552264,"uid":150031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T09:58:18.000Z","msg":"理性討論<br />\n有無人要出黎解釋下你地屌人既理據係咩?<br />\n和平理性非暴力係今日遊行集會既主場<br />\n但係點解一set rb就唔係和理非<br />\n之前和理非遊行人士太多擺雪糕筒出車路封路比遊行人士使用其實都係叫set rb<br />\n點解你地果陣又唔屌依家先黎屌?<br />\n經過呢三個月香港人既接受程度已經高左好多<br />\n就算無不反對通知書<br />\n好多和理非都願意出黎遊行集會<br />\n同埋呢一刻就算我地講到明今次既遊行集會係和理非<br />\n你以為班狗真係會當我地和理非咩?<br />\n睇下今日班狗全部著哂gear<br />\n加上港鐵玩埋不合作運動<br />\n只要人多就一定封站<br />\n就算唔set rb都遊行人士都唔會走到<br />\n所以見到個熱門post話set rb搞到和理非走唔到真係得淡笑<br />\n有無人要入黎討論下"},{"pid":"17a690d41dce7b52edd55513f9a2b7b2555ea0bc","tid":1552264,"uid":150031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T09:59:01.000Z","msg":"自推10次"},{"pid":"8d4d144f66b111de7a6cb7801440dc1f7e927266","tid":1552264,"uid":150031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T09:59:12.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"4f450d12670e935b2b9267b03cc3b6de1920a5be","tid":1552264,"uid":150031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T09:59:22.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"2aaa21bc2084865acf4c934952f60135acbcf5dd","tid":1552264,"uid":150031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T09:59:32.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"37a3a6bbfb4ffb3b7b0884dbb453e5dca3ffa616","tid":1552264,"uid":47222,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T09:59:33.000Z","msg":"班友為屌而屌"},{"pid":"95f330462d3a4306e0b201b40f89a326d2fc2de5","tid":1552264,"uid":150031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T09:59:43.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"3cbd50ec2b1052c618102beba779bcb5fa790888","tid":1552264,"uid":150031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T09:59:53.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid"